  <h1>Xpieder Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 27, 2025<br>
     <strong>Last Updated:</strong> June 27, 2025</p>

  <p>Xpieder ("we", "us", or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app, <strong>Xpieder</strong>.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>üìç Location Data</h3>
  <p>We collect your <strong>precise location</strong> to enable location-based features like discovering or pinning AR messages around real-world locations. Location is only used while the app is in use.</p>

  <h3>üì∑ Camera Access</h3>
  <p>We use your camera solely to provide <strong>augmented reality (AR)</strong> experiences. No images or videos are recorded or stored by us.</p>

  <h3>üîê Other Data</h3>
  <p>We may collect basic technical data (like device type, crash logs) to improve performance. We do not collect personal information like your name, email, or contacts, unless explicitly provided in future versions.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To enable core features like placing/viewing AR messages</li>
    <li>To provide a spatial, real-world communication experience</li>
    <li>To improve app performance, security, and usability</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not share your data</strong> with any third party. All location and AR-related data is used only within the app experience.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We store AR messages and location data temporarily or anonymously (if applicable). Users will be able to request deletion of their data in future versions.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You can revoke location or camera access at any time from your device settings. You may contact us at <strong>samhussain045@gmail.com</strong> for any privacy-related requests.</p>

  <h2>6. Security</h2>
  <p>We use modern security practices to ensure your data is transmitted securely. However, no system is 100% secure; use the app at your discretion.</p>

  <h2>7. Changes to this Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy as Xpieder evolves. We‚Äôll notify users of significant changes.</p>

